name: TechFortuneCookie
0:
”Alexa, open tech fortune cookie”
”Alexa, ask tech fortune cookie to tell me fortune number twenty four”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tech fortune cookie
des:
Alexa can be your fortune cookie! All the fun and none of the calories!

Please leave a review to make this skill more visible, and if you want to add your own sayings leave them in the comments section.

If you want to hear the same fortune again say "Please repeat", or you can ask for a specific fortune by saying, for example, "give me fortune number 24".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
